sequenceDiagram
    title Create Recovery Plan Flow
    
    participant Officer
    participant Browser
    participant SecurityFilter
    participant OfficerServlet
    participant RecoveryEJB
    participant RecoveryDAO
    participant Database
    participant EmailUtil
    participant SMTP
    
    Officer->>Browser: Navigate to Recovery Plans
    Browser->>SecurityFilter: GET /officer/recovery-plan
    SecurityFilter->>SecurityFilter: Validate session + role
    SecurityFilter->>OfficerServlet: Forward request
    OfficerServlet->>RecoveryDAO: getAllRecoveryPlans()
    RecoveryDAO->>Database: SELECT * FROM RecoveryPlans
    Database-->>RecoveryDAO: Recovery plans
    RecoveryDAO-->>OfficerServlet: List<RecoveryPlan>
    OfficerServlet-->>Browser: Render recoveryPlan.jsp
    Browser-->>Officer: Display recovery plans
    
    Officer->>Browser: Fill add plan form + Submit
    Browser->>SecurityFilter: POST /officer/add-recovery-plan
    SecurityFilter->>SecurityFilter: Validate CSRF token
    SecurityFilter->>OfficerServlet: Forward request
    OfficerServlet->>OfficerServlet: Extract parameters
    OfficerServlet->>RecoveryEJB: createRecoveryPlan(studentId, courseCode, task, deadline)
    RecoveryEJB->>RecoveryDAO: save(recoveryPlan)
    RecoveryDAO->>Database: INSERT INTO RecoveryPlans
    Database-->>RecoveryDAO: Generated ID
    RecoveryDAO-->>RecoveryEJB: RecoveryPlan with ID
    RecoveryEJB->>RecoveryEJB: sendRecoveryPlanEmail()
    RecoveryEJB->>EmailUtil: sendEmail(to, subject, body)
    EmailUtil->>SMTP: Send email via SMTP
    SMTP-->>EmailUtil: Email sent
    RecoveryEJB-->>OfficerServlet: RecoveryPlan created
    OfficerServlet-->>Browser: 302 Redirect to /officer/recovery-plan
    Browser->>SecurityFilter: GET /officer/recovery-plan
    SecurityFilter-->>Browser: Render updated page
    Browser-->>Officer: Display success message + updated list
